window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Exiled from the Five Kingdoms and pursued by the forces of Cogneid, Zenzuck and his party have a choice: double down on their relationship with the fugitive orcs of Hearthstead or break away to play the game unfettered. Neither option is truly safe, though; King Leonald hasn’t given up on the auger, and he now has access to an invincible army of conscripted players.</p> <p>Armed with new Class Skills and Zenzuck’s unique ability to get the team into trouble, the party is ready to take on anything the Boundless has to throw at them. Or, are they?</p>"; 
